Follow the tool-agnostic project rules in these files (read them; do not duplicate):

- `AGENTS.md` — build commands, CQRS/feature patterns, auth & tenant standards, and the
  mandatory Trello card workflow + build/lint gate.
- `docs/feature-invariants.md` — read the relevant section BEFORE changing code (the
  "don't break X" rules); add new invariants here after a change introduces one.
- `CLAUDE.md` — project overview/architecture (kept in sync with AGENTS.md).

Reminders:
- Backend validation/error messages in Turkish; frontend via i18n.
- Run `dotnet build backend/CityCommunicationCenter.sln` + `cd frontend && npm run build && npm run lint` before "done".
- ⚠️ Pushing `main` auto-deploys PRODUCTION; push both `main` and `master`.

Trello tooling: `scripts/trello/` (poll / move / process + Cursor `run-agent.py`).
